# A dive from mid-air onto the enemies below. Two hits of 90% each, so 180% a
# target -- which is less than Slash Blast's 183%, over fewer enemies, for a
# skill that costs a point either way. There is no real reason to use it; it is
# here because the job has it, and the combat loop will simply never pick it.
name: "Leap Attack"
kind: SKILL_KIND_ATTACK
stage: 1
max_level: 1
max_enemies: 4
lines: 2
base { skill_pct: 0.90 }
